OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782829107
OL,3,CThe defiant search for miracles in
OL,4,Cquake-hit Venezuela
OL,6,FAdditional reporting by Washington
OL,7,FProducer Joshua Brooks
OL,9,FThe defiant search for miracles
OL,10,Fcontinues in La Guaira, despite the
OL,11,Fdiminishing chances of finding any
OL,12,Fmore survivors.
OL,14,FFive days after the twin earthquakes
OL,15,Fwhich flattened dozens of apartment
OL,16,Fblocks, many Venezuelans have given up
OL,17,Fwaiting for the government to help,
OL,18,Fand are continuing the exhausting
OL,19,Fexcavation of the ruins themselves.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
