OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782829107
OL,3,CThe defiant search for miracles in
OL,4,Cquake-hit Venezuela
OL,6,FMost are working with rudimentary
OL,7,Ftools, scraping and hammering at the
OL,8,Fre-enforced concrete to look for life.
OL,10,FMany are critical of the perceived
OL,11,Fslow response of the Venezuelan
OL,12,Fgovernment and the continuing lack of
OL,13,Fcoordinated searches.
OL,15,FThere are chaotic scenes amid traffic
OL,16,Fchoked streets where many soldiers and
OL,17,Fpolice appear to be doing little to
OL,18,Fsearch the ruins.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782829107
OL,3,CThe defiant search for miracles in
OL,4,Cquake-hit Venezuela
OL,6,FThe window of opportunity to save any
OL,7,Ffurther trapped survivors is rapidly
OL,8,Fclosing, but there is little to
OL,9,Fsuggest the government is targeting
OL,10,Fthe sites where there is the greatest
OL,11,Fchance of finding life.
OL,13,FInstead, some residents have told us
OL,14,Fresources are being focused on the
OL,15,Fbuildings where government officials
OL,16,Fwere living.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782829107
OL,3,CThe defiant search for miracles in
OL,4,Cquake-hit Venezuela
OL,6,FSpeaking on Monday, the Venezuelan
OL,7,Fgovernment says they have created two
OL,8,Fcommissions, one which will evaluate
OL,9,Fthe damage and another to oversee
OL,10,Ftemporary camps.
OL,12,FInternational search and rescue groups
OL,13,Fare here, together with some US
OL,14,Fmilitary personnel, but there aren't
OL,15,Fenough to scour every downed building.
OL,17,FThe disaster has exposed the parlous
OL,18,Fstate of the socialist government's
OL,19,Femergency response after decades of
OL,20,Funder investment and sanctions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
