PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782829107
OL,3,CThe defiant search for miracles in
OL,4,Cquake-hit Venezuela
OL,6,FIt has also put a spotlight on the US
OL,7,Finvolvement here, which has in recent
OL,8,Fmonths exerted considerable influence
OL,9,Fover this country, now almost an
OL,10,FAmerican vassal state since the
OL,11,Fdeposing of President Nicholas Maduro
OL,12,Fin January.
OL,14,FDespite Donald Trump's tight grip on
OL,15,FVenezuela's leadership, it doesn't
OL,16,Fseem to have resulted in a more
OL,17,Feffective response to this crisis.
OL,19,FThe US State Department claim they
OL,20,Fhave committed more than $300 million
OL,21,Fto the Venezuelan people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
