PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782829107
OL,3,CThe defiant search for miracles in
OL,4,Cquake-hit Venezuela
OL,6,FVenezuela should be one of the world's
OL,7,Frichest countries with vast proven oil
OL,8,Freserves greater than those of Saudi
OL,9,FArabia.
OL,11,FYet this earthquake has exposed poor
OL,12,Fbuilding practices, lax regulation and
OL,13,Fa government incapable of helping its
OL,14,Fpeople in their hour of need, despite
OL,15,Fits ability to put down protests with
OL,16,Foverwhelming force.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
